body.name: Furnulem Industrial Dresser for Bedroom, Small Storage Unit Organizer with 5 Fabric Drawers and 2-Tier Side Shelves, End Table for Bedside, Nursery, Living Room, Dorm, Hallway(Rustic Brown)
deliveryMessages: Or fastest delivery Friday, February 16. Order within 6 hrs 17 mins
features: 【Sufficient 5-Drawers Storage Space】Small rustic brown drawers(NOT WOOD) provide enough storage space to store your essentials and sundries. The thick wooden top is hard-wearing and waterproof, and can hold lamps, alarm clocks, vases or other decorative items. Drawers are suitable for organizing clothes, toys, socks, underwear, scarves, blankets, etc.

【Exquisite Craftsmanship】The closet dresser is made of steel and wood construction. All wood panels are made from high-grade MDF for a solid structure and excellent workmanship to meet your quest for quality. Foldable rustic fabric drawers(Not Wood) are lightweight and easy to pull out and push in.

【Stunning Partition Design】Multi-functional partition design meets your various storage needs. The left side of the nightstand is designed with two shelves for displaying your decorations. The right side is designed with an anti-item tipping backboard for displaying some books, photo frames, etc. The drawers are used to store some privacy items.

【Versatile Usage Dresser】This dresser unit organizer with drawers can be applied to compact spaces such as bedrooms, living rooms, hallways, guest room, closet, nursery, entryway, small apartment, dormitories, office etc. in multiple scenes, which can be used as bedside storage night stand, lingerie nightstand, chest of drawers, sofa end table, office supplies storage drawers, makeup vanity, kids nightstand, or baby nursery table, etc.

【Easy Assembly】The package contains all the accessories and hardware kits as well as the instructions that are shipped with this product. The instruction manual is easy to understand with clear step-by-step and logical illustrations and the user only needs to follow the steps to complete the installation with ease.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 26, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Lightweight nice size
reviews.reviewText: I like this furniture set, it is light weight and very easy to assemble. I did two of these while watching a movie. It looks good in the room and looks like it is made of something sturdier. I am impressed by how much I can easily fit stuff into these, definitely recommend if you have an apartment or small space where lighter furniture works well!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Exactly what I was looking for!
reviews.reviewText: Got this for my toddler’s small bedroom. It fit in nicely and the quality is not bad for the price. Also, easy to build!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 1, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Nice storage shelf.
reviews.reviewText: It's pretty nice. Ease of putting together was decent. Instructions were definitely translated from another language....it instructed me to put one side opposite and I didn't realize til I was almost done and had to undo my work to fix. But overall a good product for the price point. Would by another.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 16, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy and cute
reviews.reviewText: This is a super compact, lightweight sturdy storage and organisation solution for small spaces. The hard front on the draws makes them feel more substantial and reduces risk of opening and shutting causing the handle screws to widen the holes and come out as I’ve found with other fabric drawers. I love how it looks in my son’s nursery

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good nightstand for the price!
reviews.reviewText: I like how easy this nightstand went together. Having a drill helped assemble this thing faster too. One important thing to note is that the drawers aren’t made of wood… it’s also kinda small but it is perfect for what I need it to do. It looks really good too!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 21, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Very easily to build and pretty sturdy! I use it as a place to put all my dogs stuff. Very high quality too!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 28, 2023
reviews.reviewText: So the actual little nightstand I like it’s cute it matches perfectly with my desk. The only thing is that once I was almost done assembling it I realized that. The step I was on in the instructions was difficult because I didn’t have one of the pieces necessary for the drawer to be able to slide in and out. I had to right pieces instead of one left and one right. Other than that there weren’t any issues really. Please be more careful when packing up the things in the box thank you.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Came rusty; was hard to assemble
reviews.reviewText: Obnoxious to assemble and arrived rusty but I kept it because taking it apart would’ve been a huge pain in the butt and it was…fine. Very small. Not really worth it.
